item.title: G.R.L. - Ugly Heart
item.description: This song belongs to G.R.L so buy their CDs. In this version I plant the 1st and 2nd fingers for three chords: A, D and F#m.

item.title: G.R.L. - Ugly Heart
item.description: This song belongs to GRL so buy their CDs It's a nice song with no inappropriate messages, (rare these days) and it essentially says don't put up with someone who has an ugly heart.
